        <caption><title>Box 1.</title><p>A boxed note with its own paragraph.</p></caption>
        <p>Boxed content can contain <bold>important</bold> callouts.</p>
      </boxed-text>
      <preformat preformat-type="code" xml:space="preserve">const reader = "BitLibrary";
console.log(reader);</preformat>
      <preformat preformat-type="mermaid" xml:space="preserve">flowchart TD
A[Find XML endpoint] --&gt; B{Has graphic?}
B --&gt; C[Render image figure]
B --&gt; D[Render formatted flowchart source]</preformat>
